Eric Ntumba, Director in charge of Southern DRC at Equity BCDC catches up with Laura Cornish, Editor-In-Chief of Mining Review Africa at DRC Mining Week 2022, and chats about the prominent position the bank holds in the DRC, its financing options for artisanal miners and its ongoing commitment to focus on miners with a responsible ESG ethic. This video can be viewed in French by adjusting the closed caption and setting options.